Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.51,0:00:09.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Attack with Canon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:11.51,Main,,0,0,0,,End turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.51,0:00:14.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Dang you're strong, Kazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:18.52,Main,,0,0,0,,C'mon, one more battle!\NI'm not going to quit until I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:20.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, that just means\Nyou won't go home tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.69,0:00:22.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:25.48,Main,,0,0,0,,So, you're finally away from your sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:26.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:29.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't say it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.53,0:00:31.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys? Can we join too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:36.70,Main,,0,0,0,,We started WIXOSS too,\Nbut it's kind of hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:39.29,Main,,0,0,0,,You're good at this, right Kazuki-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.29,0:00:40.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.87,0:00:43.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, can you teach me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.38,0:00:45.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:05.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The truth rests solely on{\i0}\N{\i1}the front/back of a card{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:10.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It has not yet been solved{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:21.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Upon the dazzling, dizzying stage,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:32.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}destroy those entangled emotions{\i0}\N{\i1}as many times as it takes to satisfy you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:37.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should the tomorrows{\i0}\N{\i1}wandering after fate's beckoning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:42.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}choose and discard so that{\i0}\N{\i1}they can become one?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't afford to disclose my reproachable hand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:53.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The days spent draining{\i0}\N{\i1}the already-dry sea of regret{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.49,0:01:58.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}desire within limited words forgiveness{\i0}\N{\i1}for the unplanned smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.91,0:02:03.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't mind forgetting reality{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.79,0:02:08.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to know anything now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:10.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:17.76,Main,,0,0,0,,"WIXOSS Official Tournament"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:19.60,Main,,0,0,0,,"Grand prize to be awarded\Nto the winner of the tournament!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:21.35,Main,,0,0,0,,WIXOSS Party?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:23.64,Main,,0,0,0,,It's more like a place\Nfor people to get together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:29.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Only the guys used to participate,\Nbut there are a lot of girls attending now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.27,0:02:33.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I know! Why don't you three attend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:38.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, maybe make matching clothes.\NIt'll be cute! I'll help too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:40.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Momoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:44.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:49.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you can enter on that day,\Nso why not go and take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.38,0:02:51.13,Main,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:56.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm almost finished. So just a sec more, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:02:59.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:03.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah... So about the tournament,\Nwhat do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:13.03,Main,,0,0,0,,A person without a wish participating\Nin WIXOSS as a Selector...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.03,0:03:14.44,Main,,0,0,0,,...is blasphemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:18.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:22.08,Main,,0,0,0,,There may be Selectors there, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:24.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:26.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, your wish already came true...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:28.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:31.88,Main,,0,0,0,,And if I win...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:34.25,Main,,0,0,0,,...that would be mean to the other person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:36.93,Main,,0,0,0,,It should be okay if the person\Nyou face isn't a Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:39.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Plus, with the guys,\Nwe can battle them all we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! I can battle anyone\Nas long as they're not Selectors!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:46.02,Main,,0,0,0,,--Yeah!\N--All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:49.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I guess I'll enter too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:52.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to test my new deck anyways...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:54.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Right, Midoriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:57.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Midoriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:03:59.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh...? Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:03.78,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, it's settled!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:12.09,Main,,0,0,0,,So, what do you want to do?\NSince we're going, why not match our clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:14.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Y'know, like an idol. Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:17.67,Main,,0,0,0,,But, these clothes are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:19.68,Main,,0,0,0,,"Tunic"\N"Wide-Necked Pull-over"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:22.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they would cost this much... Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:24.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:27.23,Main,,0,0,0,,"Only for a limited time"\NWhoa! It's so cheap! It's only 100 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:30.69,Main,,0,0,0,,There are all sorts here.\NHow about we coordinate with these?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:31.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Scrunchies?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:34.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Right! Buying clothes may be too much, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:36.40,Main,,0,0,0,,...how's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:38.49,Main,,0,0,0,,It's green so I thought it'll match you, Hitoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:40.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:45.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Then I'm red! Ruko, you're white...\Nbut there's none here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:47.33,Main,,0,0,0,,...you take this strange-colored one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:49.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want that icky-colored one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:49.83,Main,,0,0,0,,How about this then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:53.29,Main,,0,0,0,,It's still icky! Come on, Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:55.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:59.34,Main,,0,0,0,,So, we bought these matching... and then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:02.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe? I know you're happy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:07.18,Main,,0,0,0,,...you just came out of the shower.\NYour hair is going to get kinked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:08.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:10.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, and Ruko was about to get
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:14.02,Main,,0,0,0,,a really weird-colored one, but she ended up\Nhaving an aqua-colored one, and...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:16.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, we can talk about it later, but first,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:20.36,Main,,0,0,0,,wear something warm and dry\Nyour hair so you don't catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:21.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:28.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah... It's kinked...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:32.83,Main,,0,0,0,,The scrunchie is a bit wet too...\NWell, that's obvious...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:35.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm such an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:36.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:38.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:40.59,Main,,0,0,0,,It's best you get rid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:43.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Get... rid of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:45.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Your wish already came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:48.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You have no need to battle now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:55.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-That may be so, but not battling isn't\Na reason for me to get rid of you, Midoriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:57.69,Main,,0,0,0,,If you keep me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:06:00.61,Main,,0,0,0,,...something terrible may happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:04.57,Main,,0,0,0,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:10.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko and Yuzuki aren't the only ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:13.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Midoriko, you're my precious friend too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:15.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:20.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, stop saying weird things like that.\NWhere is that dryer now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:29.56,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't working...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:31.02,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:32.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:35.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I figured I could tie my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:39.06,Main,,0,0,0,,But, you're kind of clumsy.\NHere, let me tie it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:42.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? D-Don't worry...! I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:45.15,Main,,0,0,0,,--But, Yuzuki...\N--I'm fine! I can do it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:51.08,Main,,0,0,0,,It's so cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:55.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:57.63,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a giraffe on the pillar now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:07:02.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Giraffe! It's going to battle that giraffe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:06.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, all you think about is battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:08.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:09.85,Main,,0,0,0,,...do it with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:19.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona was really pretty,\Nbut... she was kind of scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll beat the scaries!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:36.83,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks like I'm here a bit early...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:41.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm here... I'll be waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:42.34,Main,,0,0,0,,"To: Yuzuki" "I'm here, I'll be waiting."\NI'm here... I'll be waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:43.71,Main,,0,0,0,,"Sending"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:53.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Waiting here with so many people around...\NI feel like any other girl now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:56.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe, you are like any other girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:58.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Heh, well, I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.57,Main,,0,0,0,,The weather is so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:09.11,Main,,0,0,0,,When I moved to Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:13.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought there wasn't much of a sky\Nto look at with all these buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:18.33,Main,,0,0,0,,But, the sky is there... It's blue like any other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:22.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I notice...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:23.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Was I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:27.13,Main,,0,0,0,,...looking down all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:29.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:35.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:38.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Please! Get rid of me! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:44.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:47.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! There were so many\Npeople in the restroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:50.57,Main,,0,0,0,,and the kid behind me was\Nsaying she was about to leak, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:52.20,Main,,0,0,0,,We're making Hitoe wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:56.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:58.71,Main,,0,0,0,,There are so many people here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:06.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:08.09,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:10.34,Main,,0,0,0,,She's not replying back to my email either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:13.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she got angry\Nbecause we were late...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.22,0:09:16.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe's not the type to get angry with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:18.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so too, Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:20.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:22.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:23.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:25.77,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:29.19,Main,,0,0,0,,A battle field opened somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:30.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:32.03,Main,,0,0,0,,...Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:42.33,Main,,0,0,0,,The opponent is... so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:46.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Midoriko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:49.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:50.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Midoriko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:56.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't let you suffer anymore...\NI'll try to lose as soon as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:58.01,Main,,0,0,0,,No! Don't give up, Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:03.02,Main,,0,0,0,,No, it's okay.\NMy wish already came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:07.02,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no need to go\Nthrough painful battles now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:10.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:13.36,Main,,0,0,0,,There's something I didn't tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:15.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Midoriko...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:19.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you that you can become\Nan Eternal Girl if you win three times...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:22.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:24.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:28.13,Main,,0,0,0,,--W-We're sorry...\N--Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.13,0:10:32.51,Main,,0,0,0,,But, if you lose three times...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:05.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it around here, Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:09.71,Main,,0,0,0,,The battle field... is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:10.59,Main,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:13.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}? Do you know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:17.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:26.14,Main,,0,0,0,,--Hitoe!\N--Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:28.27,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NWe were looking all over for...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:32.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:36.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:39.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do you know my name...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:41.87,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:43.24,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:47.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:57.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe... Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:04.52,Main,,0,0,0,,No! Don't touch Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:07.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:09.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:10.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:13.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:17.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't sense Hitoe's rights as a Selector.\NShe lost the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:18.86,Main,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:21.37,Main,,0,0,0,,She's not a Selector?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:26.79,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this about?! Why is Hitoe like that?!\NDoes it have to do with her losing three times?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:30.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:36.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Lose three times, and not only\Ndo you lose your wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:40.01,Main,,0,0,0,,...that very wish is reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:41.80,Main,,0,0,0,,The wish... reversed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:42.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:46.85,Main,,0,0,0,,If your wish was to be wealthy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:54.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Losing in battle means that you lose\Nall wealth, and are plummeted to poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:13:00.45,Main,,0,0,0,,If your wish was to become\Nskilled in playing the piano...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:04.99,Main,,0,0,0,,You may lose your piano, or you may\Nbecome incapable of playing the piano...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:08.46,Main,,0,0,0,,In any case, you won't be able\Nto play the piano, forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:10.50,Main,,0,0,0,,That's horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:14.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not getting this...\NSo, what happened to Hitoe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:18.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe's wish was "to make friends"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:21.59,Main,,0,0,0,,With that wish reversed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:24.68,Main,,0,0,0,,She loses... her friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:28.52,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:31.35,Main,,0,0,0,,She will never make friends, ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:33.98,Main,,0,0,0,,You saw what happened there with Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:38.69,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems if anyone has\Na potential to be her friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:41.70,Main,,0,0,0,,...her body reacts with pain\Nwhen they try to approach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:42.78,Main,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:46.03,Main,,0,0,0,,And with the third loss...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:49.75,Main,,0,0,0,,...the battle for her wish ends...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:54.54,Main,,0,0,0,,All memories she had towards\Nbeing a Selector disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:14:00.42,Main,,0,0,0,,It's so scary... Scary... Scary...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:04.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:08.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Who... were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,It didn't hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:20.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:27.95,Main,,0,0,0,,It hurts... Hurts... Hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:34.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Scary... Don't want to think... Don't want to...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:45.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I've decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:49.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll wish for Hitoe to be back to normal again!\NThat will be my wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:51.39,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right! That would...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:52.85,Main,,0,0,0,,That won't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:15:02.90,Main,,0,0,0,,With the battle as a Selector, all wishes,\Nwhether it be granted or not, cannot be undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:04.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:08.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did you keep such an\Nimportant thing a secret?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:12.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you answering me?! Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:32.14,Main,,0,0,0,,The sky got cloudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:34.27,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's going to rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:38.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't have the right to cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:43.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I took your heartfelt wish away from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:58.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I liked you, Hitoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:16:03.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe... I wish I wasn't your LRIG...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:07.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Good-bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:36.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of you now, Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:39.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I believed in you all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:44.84,Main,,0,0,0,,You can get rid of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:49.05,Main,,0,0,0,,It's fine, Yuzuki... You can throw me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:50.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:56.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:57.85,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:00.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh... No, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:02.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Were you fighting with Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:08.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki... you've been acting strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:13.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You used to speak to me about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:14.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Not everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:18.37,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I want you to speak to me,\Nrely on me like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:20.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't say my true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:22.96,Main,,0,0,0,,We've been together all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.96,0:17:25.13,Main,,0,0,0,,If I say it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:30.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:34.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing... No, really I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:39.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess... you don't want to tell me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:45.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I... I'll be fine, by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:48.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazu--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:53.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello? Oh, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:57.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow? With everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:02.16,Main,,0,0,0,,No, that's okay, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.17,0:18:05.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:07.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Right... Okay then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:14.43,Main,,0,0,0,,No... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:21.23,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the first time Tama\Ncame to this kind of store.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:26.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I only come to these kinds of\Nrestaurants with Grandma, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:29.40,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:31.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma's really smart...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:35.32,Main,,0,0,0,,She can find out right away if I'm\Nhiding my failed tests and things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:36.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:41.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:43.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama don't know a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:48.21,Main,,0,0,0,,There's something white\Nin my head. I can't think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:53.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama likes to battle! I want\Nto do more! Plenty more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:56.43,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I don't like Ru sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:58.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:19:00.52,Main,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:04.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Piruluk told me that there\Nwas a battle around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:09.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought it could be Ru-ru and the gals,\Nso I sent an email to Yuzu-pon and Hitoe, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:12.07,Main,,0,0,0,,...only Hitoe's one came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:18.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Funny thing is, she doesn't remember a thing!\NI guess she's not a Selector any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:21.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you know this was going to\Nhappen if you lose, Akira-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:24.00,Main,,0,0,0,,--What...?\N--What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:25.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:28.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's tinkle together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:29.88,Main,,0,0,0,,A-Akira-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:34.92,Main,,0,0,0,,The first battle field I encountered\Nwasn't my own battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:36.51,Main,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:42.68,Main,,0,0,0,,On my way out from the shoot, Iona was\Njust about to battle another Selector,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:45.89,Main,,0,0,0,,and I got pulled into that field.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:52.90,Main,,0,0,0,,The opposing Selector already lost two battles,\Nand was at her last straw.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:59.87,Main,,0,0,0,,It looked like she was sick, and was like,\Nhuffing and puffing to try and win the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:05.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, Iona still beat up\Nthat tragic heroine real bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:16.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, she suffered a bad stroke and\Nan ambulance came--it was just total chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:21.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Her LRIG's quite sadistic, y'know? Poor girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:23.68,Main,,0,0,0,,S-So what happened to that girl...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:29.81,Main,,0,0,0,,How should I know? She was taken\Nto the hospital. But, at that rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:33.48,Main,,0,0,0,,That's... terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:37.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, seriously, right? Compared to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:41.49,Main,,0,0,0,,...not being able to make friends\Never again, is like... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:43.20,Main,,0,0,0,,H-How did you know...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:48.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I saw her wish in battle the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:52.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, not that it matters since\NHitoe was a hyper-loner anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:56.38,Main,,0,0,0,,But, you should be happy! Now you\Ndon't have to bother with her slowness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:59.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru-ru, you would've been teased with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:02.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, and Hitoe now knows\Nwhat she can and can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:06.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, she's totally impossible. Totally gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:08.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if she doesn't ever make friends again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:11.19,Main,,0,0,0,,...it'll be no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:14.15,Main,,0,0,0,,No problem...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:15.61,Main,,0,0,0,,--Yup! So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.61,0:21:17.19,Main,,0,0,0,,--Take that back...!\N--Yup! So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.69,0:21:21.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Nopey-nopey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:26.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Take that back! If you don't...\NI'm not going to forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:29.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Forgive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:34.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, it doesn't matter if Ru-ru forgives me\Nor not. That doesn't faze good old, Aki-lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:42.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, if you really can't\Nforgive me, then let's battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:48.43,Main,,0,0,0,,If you beat me up, maybe I'll\Ntotally feel like apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:49.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:50.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:55.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll battle... And, I'll make\Nyou apologize to Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.82,0:21:58.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll make you apologize to my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:14.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nodding to the clockwork shadow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:19.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}opens the door to the end,{\i0}\N{\i1}bringing in the darkness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:25.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There we catch glimpses of the perilous answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.64,0:22:31.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today's prayer becomes taboo tomorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:37.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The upside-down maze reflects{\i0}\N{\i1}the heavens and the earth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.23,0:22:43.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The gear begins to turn{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.15,0:22:49.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen carefully among the masses{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:59.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and that bell resounding in{\i0}\N{\i1}the skies beckons the soul...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:06.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must move forward even beyond eternity{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.68,0:23:12.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because it is the future I chose{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The unreachable summer clouds{\i0}\N{\i1}and flickering heat haze{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:25.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day I'll get back my place of smiles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.83,0:23:35.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe lost three times...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.66,0:23:37.33,Main,,0,0,0,,You're so horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:38.63,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.63,0:23:41.00,Main,,0,0,0,,No... No, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:42.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.30,0:23:44.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared of anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.67,0:23:46.97,Main,,0,0,0,,"This Pure Heart."
